      <title>泰晤士水务公司预计修订计划下水费将上涨 59%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/thames-water-says-regulator-s-proposed-cuts-make-it-uninvestible</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务有限公司 (Thames Water Utilities Ltd.) 表示，由于负债累累的公用事业公司竞相吸引投资者以维持运营，到本世纪末其账单将不得不增加 59%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/thames-water-says-regulator-s-proposed-cuts-make-it-uninvestible</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 12:03:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
